@startuml UC1_Register
title UC1 - Register
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fredoslav2004/MinimalThemePUML/refs/heads/main/minimal-theme.puml

actor User
participant System

User -> System: Initiate registration
System --> User: Request user details
User -> System: Provide username and password
System -> System: Validate user details
alt Success
    System --> User: Confirm registration and log the user in
else Failure
    System --> User: Show error message
end
@enduml
